text: Günther Bauch (born 30 April 1939) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle middleweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Halle (Saale)
